#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.23:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Nānātitthiyavagga "
msgstr "3. Various Sectarians "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Serīsutta "
msgstr "23. With Serī "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn2.23:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho serī devaputto bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Standing to one side, the god Serī addressed the Buddha in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.133, sc2
msgctxt "sn2.23:2.1"
msgid "“Annamevābhinandanti, "
msgstr "“Both gods and humans "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:2.2"
msgid "ubhaye devamānusā; "
msgstr "enjoy their food. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:2.3"
msgid "Atha ko nāma so yakkho, "
msgstr "So what’s the name of the spirit "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:2.4"
msgid "yaṃ annaṃ nābhinandatī”ti. "
msgstr "who doesn’t like food?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn2.23:3.1"
msgid "“Ye naṃ dadanti saddhāya, "
msgstr "“Those who give with faith "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:3.2"
msgid "vippasannena cetasā; "
msgstr "and a clear and confident heart, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:3.3"
msgid "Tameva annaṃ bhajati, "
msgstr "partake of food "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:3.4"
msgid "asmiṃ loke paramhi ca. "
msgstr "in this world and the next. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn2.23:4.1"
msgid "Tasmā vineyya maccheraṃ, "
msgstr "So you should dispel stinginess, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:4.2"
msgid "dajjā dānaṃ malābhibhū; "
msgstr "overcoming that stain, and give a gift. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:4.3"
msgid "Puññāni paralokasmiṃ, "
msgstr "The good deeds of sentient beings "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:4.4"
msgid "patiṭṭhā honti pāṇinan”ti. "
msgstr "support them in the next world.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.58, sc5
msgctxt "sn2.23:5.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing, "

msgctxt "sn2.23:5.2"
msgid "Yāvasubhāsitamidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā: "
msgstr "how well said this was by Master Gotama. He repeated the Buddha’s verses, and said: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn2.23:6.1"
msgid "‘Ye naṃ dadanti saddhāya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:6.2"
msgid "vippasannena cetasā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:6.3"
msgid "Tameva annaṃ bhajati, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.23:6.4"
msgid "asmiṃ loke paramhi ca. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
