msgstr "When they say, “We would give gifts”, what am I to say?’ "

msgctxt "sn2.23:11.7"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, bhante, catutthaṃ dvāraṃ brāhmaṇagahapatikānaṃ adāsiṃ. "
msgstr "And so I gave the fourth gate to my brahmins and householders. "

msgctxt "sn2.23:11.8"
msgid "Tattha brāhmaṇagahapatikānaṃ dānaṃ dīyittha, mama dānaṃ paṭikkami. "
msgstr "There they gave gifts, while my own giving dwindled. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.137, sc12
msgctxt "sn2.23:12.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, bhante, purisā upasaṅkamitvā etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then my men approached me and said, "

msgctxt "sn2.23:12.2"
msgid "‘na kho dāni devassa koci dānaṃ dīyatī’ti. "
msgstr "‘Now Your Majesty is not giving gifts at all!’ "

msgctxt "sn2.23:12.3"
msgid "Evaṃ vuttāhaṃ, bhante, te purise etadavocaṃ: "
msgstr "When they said this, I said to those men, "

# NOTE: I’m not clear whether this means “give half of that half “or” give that half”.
msgctxt "sn2.23:12.4"
msgid "‘tena hi, bhaṇe, yo bāhiresu janapadesu āyo sañjāyati tato upaḍḍhaṃ antepure pavesetha, upaḍḍhaṃ tattheva dānaṃ detha samaṇabrāhmaṇakapaṇaddhikavanibbakayācakānan’ti. "
msgstr "‘So then, my men, send half of the revenue from the outer districts to the royal compound. Then give half right there to ascetics and brahmins, to paupers, vagrants, travelers, and beggars.’ "

msgctxt "sn2.23:12.5"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, bhante, evaṃ dīgharattaṃ katānaṃ puññānaṃ evaṃ dīgharattaṃ katānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pariyantaṃ nādhigacchāmi—"
msgstr "Sir, for a long time I made so much merit and did so many skillful deeds. I never reached any limit so as to say "

msgctxt "sn2.23:12.6"
msgid "ettakaṃ puññanti vā ettako puññavipākoti vā ettakaṃ sagge ṭhātabbanti vāti. "
msgstr "‘there’s this much merit’ or ‘there’s this much result of merit’ or ‘for so long I’ll remain in heaven’. "

msgctxt "sn2.23:12.7"
msgid "Acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante. "
msgstr "It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing, "

msgctxt "sn2.23:12.8"
msgid "Yāvasubhāsitamidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā: "
msgstr "how well said this was by Master Gotama: "

